    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>In this post I&rsquo;ll be explaning why and how I&rsquo;m using octopress in this site, maybe it will help someone but mainly it will help me remember the process and changes in the future.</p></blockquote>

<p>It took me over a month to slowly understand what octopress is and what was the best option for me to install and deploy it.</p>

<p>Finally I chose Github Pages&hellip;</p>

<p>Install</p>

